short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Undo your last missclick on a youtube video

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension fixes the infuriating problem of accidentally skipping places in a YouTube video. A simple undo button is added to the YouTube player, pressing it will jump you to the last time you skipped.
